text: Vakhtang Gomelauri (, born 24 December 1974) is a Georgian politician, who is the current Minister of Internal Affairs of Georgia. He was head of the State Security Service of Georgia from 25 July 2015 to 9 September 2019. == References == Category:1974 births Category:Politicians from Tbilisi Category:Living people
title: Vakhtang Gomelauri
